<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Échéance proche - RHPro</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #fcf9f6; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
    <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="table-layout: fixed;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 0;">
                <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="600" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;">
                    <!-- Header -->
                    <tr>
                        <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 40px 20px 40px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%);">
                            <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center; line-height: 64px; font-size: 32px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
                                ⏳
                            </div>
                            <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">Échéance Proche</h1>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Body -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 40px;">
                            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #4b5563; margin-top: 0;">Bonjour <strong>{{ employe.prenom }}</strong>,</p>
                            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6;">Nous attirons votre attention sur la tâche suivante qui arrive bientôt à son terme. Il ne vous reste que <strong>{{ daysLeft }} jour(s)</strong>.</p>
                            
                            <!-- Task Card -->
                            <div style="background-color: #fffbeb; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; border: 1px solid #fef3c7; margin: 30px 0;">
                                <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                                    <tr>
                                        <td style="padding-bottom: 8px;">
                                            <span style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #d97706; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">Projet</span>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td style="padding-bottom: 20px;">
                                            <span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #1e293b;">{{ tache.projet.titre }}</span>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td style="padding-bottom: 8px;">
                                            <span style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #d97706; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">Tâche</span>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td style="padding-bottom: 20px;">
                                            <span style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; color: #334155;">{{ tache.titre }}</span>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td style="padding-top: 10px; border-top: 1px solid #fde68a;">
                                            <span style="font-size: 14px; color: #92400e;">📅 Échéance : <strong>{{ tache.dateFin|date('d/m/Y') }}</strong></span>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                </table>
                            </div>

                            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.6;">Si vous avez besoin de plus de temps, n'hésitez pas à en parler avec votre responsable RH.</p>
                            
                            <!-- Action Button -->
                            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;">
                                <a href="http://127.0.0.1:8000/projet" style="background-color: #f59e0b; color: #ffffff; padding: 16px 32px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);">Accéder à mon tableau de bord</a>
                            </div>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Footer -->
                    <tr>
                        <td align="center" style="padding: 30px 40px; background-color: #fcf9f6; border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9;">
                            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; font-weight: 500;">
                                RHPro - Notification Automatique de Performance
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
